  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Coat a baking dish with butter.",
    "Chop the cashew nuts into small pieces and mix them with the melted butter, maple syrup or honey, ground cinnamon, and vanilla extract. Mix well until it forms an evenly distributed mixture without clumping.",
    "Pour the crumble mixture into the prepared baking dish.",
    "Bake in preheated oven for 20 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
    "Let cool slightly before serving."
